{"sectionId":758,"sectionIdLiteral":"758","humanId":"lesson-335","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I choose to see my brother‚Äôs sinlessness.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 335"},"annotation":"W-335","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-335\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"758#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Forgiveness is a choice.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>I never see my brother as he is, for that is far beyond perception.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>What I see in him is merely what I wish to see, because it stands for what I want to be the truth.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>It is to this alone that I respond, however much I seem to be impelled by outside happenings.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>I choose to see what I would look upon, and this I see, and only this.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>My brother‚Äôs sinlessness shows me that I would look upon my own.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>And I will see it, having chosen to behold my brother in its holy light.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"758#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>What could restore Your memory to me, except to see my brother‚Äôs sinlessness?</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>His holiness reminds me that he was created one with me, and like myself.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"758#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>In him I find my Self, and in Your Son I find the memory of You as well.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Forgiveness is a choice. I never see my brother as he is, for that is far beyond perception. What I see in him is merely what I wish to see, because it stands for what I want to be the truth. It is","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 335: I choose to see my brother‚Äôs‚Ä¶ | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†335 ‚ÄúI choose to see my brother‚Äôs sinlessness‚Äù: Forgiveness is a choice. I never see my brother as he is, for that is far‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 335","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":758,"slugs":["lesson-335","i-choose-to-see-my-brothers-sinlessness"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 335","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":758,"slugs":["lesson-335","i-choose-to-see-my-brothers-sinlessness"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 335","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":758,"slugs":["lesson-335","i-choose-to-see-my-brothers-sinlessness"]}}],"slug